g.text: I HAVE READ, UNDERSTOOD, AND AGREED TO THE RULES
PERMIT MUST BE PLACED AND CLEARLY VISIBLE ON DASHBOARD FACING THIS SIDE UP
be filled out using bold black ink only.
Month and day should be filled out on the date you cut your tree.
be present at time of tree cutting.
cut tree tops off - take the whole tree.
Leave no trace - pack it in, pack it out.
be on National Forest land when cutting your Christmas tree(s)
It is unlawful to reuse or duplicate this permit for the purpose of removing
more products than the permit holder has purchased.
FILL IN THE MONTH AND DAY YOU CUT YOUR TREE(S)
